     "Organizations must build and continuously update a comprehensive inventory of all enterprise assets, both hardware and software, connected to the infrastructure. This inventory forms the foundation for nearly every other security control, as you cannot protect what you don't know exists. Assets should be tracked with attributes including owner, location, and classification.",
     "Use an asset management platform or CMDB to record all devices. Integrate with DHCP, Active Directory, and network scanning tools to auto-populate and reconcile the inventory at least monthly.",
