     "Export account lists from Active Directory, cloud IAM, and application directories regularly. Compare against HR records to identify accounts for users who have left or changed roles.",
     "Use an identity governance platform (e.g., SailPoint, Saviynt) or AD reports to generate a full account inventory and reconcile against HR data on a monthly basis.",
